{"tid":312295,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[真正勞資糾紛] 文青女神袁澧林被指違約擅自接工作　遭經理人公司入稟控告","createTime":"2017-07-07T10:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T05:56:14.000Z","uid":63998,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"040dc5ddcc307a1f312c1ba7a2a887df6c759cb1","tid":312295,"uid":63998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"有「ViuTV女神」之稱藝人袁澧林（Angela），遭經理人公司入稟高等法院，控告她在未經經理人安排而擅自接洽工作，違反合約，要求她交出所賺取的酬勞及賠償。<br />\n<br />\n原告Starz People (HK) Limited於入稟狀指，原告與被告袁澧林在2015年5月簽訂經理人合約，為期3年，直至2018年8月，合約訂明原告是袁的唯一獨家經理人，負責接洽及安排她所有關於電視、電影、話劇、雜誌拍攝、電台廣泛等等的娛樂事業工作。<br />\n<br />\n但袁卻違反合約，故原告要求法庭聲明合約至2018年8月6日前仍然有效，並禁止袁私下接洽工作，以及交待私下接洽的帳目及費用。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA 1597/2017<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/103167?utm_content=buffer98e9d&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F103167%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer98e9d%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=XLERuoKmfOBi6k80zs%2BHnb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=4b83edf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/103167?utm_content=buffer98e9d&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a>"},{"pid":"feaaac621cba836ca29f5421c9401de993fae49d","tid":312295,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />私下接"},{"pid":"418132c95f7d238c6d97f43a7b277ec75275aaf7","tid":312295,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"冇叫解 但呢啲新聞令人好尷尬"},{"pid":"18b10c83bdd0d85e8bdc4904e45bfe5fa05d56de","tid":312295,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:56:14.000Z","msg":"抵"}]}